metadata.description: A Return of the Originals event! 'The Lady and the Spider'. A tale told in widevision! Be here for a HOT TIME in the DEAD TOWN tonight! A catastrophe puts The Spider in the arms of lovely Domino Lady. Be here for the first time the Master of Men and the Sexy Avenger ignite the comic pages, as they deal with spontaneous flaming zombies!
metadata.name: The Spider & Lady Domino
